INSERT INTO `cr_car_reviews` VALUES (1,'Outstanding rental experience! Incredible fuel efficiency saved us money The car was absolutely pristine and handled like a dream on every road. The staff went above and beyond to help us Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,26,58,NULL,'published','2025-07-19 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(2,'Average rental experience. The vehicle met basic expectations The pickup process took a while but the car was clean. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,25,97,NULL,'published','2025-12-20 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(3,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Quick and easy pickup process Would definitely recommend to others Just a small issue with a small scuff on the rear bumper but nothing major.',4,15,26,NULL,'published','2025-12-01 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(4,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine The customer service was world-class Incredible bang for your buck Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,1,35,NULL,'published','2025-09-05 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(5,'Disappointing rental experience. The overall value proposition was problematic and The air conditioning wasn\'t working properly. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,20,90,NULL,'published','2025-03-27 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(6,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly Started every time without hesitation Made our vacation stress-free and enjoyable Will book with them again for sure.',4,13,77,NULL,'published','2024-09-20 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(7,'Perfect car for our business trip! The seats were like luxury recliners The performance was absolutely flawless Exceptional attention to customer needs Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,25,47,NULL,'published','2025-07-20 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(8,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly Completely dependable for our entire trip Reliable transportation for our family trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,19,57,NULL,'published','2025-05-01 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(9,'Great rental experience! Spacious interior The car was very reliable and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. The pickup process took a while but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,26,62,NULL,'published','2025-09-12 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(10,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Incredibly comfortable for long drives The car felt stable and well-balanced Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,26,50,NULL,'published','2025-09-15 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(11,'Absolutely fantastic! State-of-the-art amenities throughout Reliability that exceeded all expectations This rental exceeded every expectation This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,4,36,NULL,'published','2025-08-14 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(12,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the overall condition was satisfactory but the customer service could be improved. Standard rental experience Fair value for money.',3,14,9,NULL,'published','2024-10-25 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(13,'Outstanding rental experience! Incredible fuel efficiency saved us money The car was showroom quality and provided effortless acceleration. The team was absolutely wonderful to work with Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,11,32,NULL,'published','2025-10-02 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(14,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable The engine performed well on both city and highway Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,18,13,NULL,'published','2025-06-24 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(15,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Started every time without hesitation Reliable transportation for our family trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,14,33,NULL,'published','2025-09-20 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(16,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Plenty of legroom for everyone Good handling in various driving conditions Handled the mountain roads beautifully Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,5,23,NULL,'published','2025-04-01 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(17,'Excellent value for money. The infotainment system was user-friendly No unexpected problems or breakdowns Enhanced our weekend getaway experience Will book with them again for sure.',4,1,96,NULL,'published','2025-12-23 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(18,'Very pleased with this rental. The build quality was impressive Quick and easy pickup process Would definitely recommend to others Just a small issue with the pickup location being slightly hard to find but nothing major.',4,12,24,NULL,'published','2025-01-05 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(19,'Very disappointed. The overall build quality was poor The engine was not functioning properly and it felt unstable at highway speeds. Not worth the money at all.',1,4,84,NULL,'published','2025-08-25 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(20,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the fuel economy exceeded expectations but the customer service could be improved. Adequate for basic transportation needs Fair value for money.',3,20,47,NULL,'published','2024-12-20 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(21,'Outstanding rental experience! Advanced safety features gave us confidence The car was showroom quality and handled like a dream on every road. Incredibly professional and courteous service Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,5,61,NULL,'published','2024-03-26 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(22,'Absolutely fantastic! Advanced capabilities that impressed everyone Not a single issue throughout our entire rental The best rental car experience we\'ve ever had This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,23,57,NULL,'published','2025-08-04 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(23,'Perfect car for our family road trip! Every passenger commented on the amazing comfort Exceptional driving dynamics in all conditions Staff went above and beyond at every step Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,23,10,NULL,'published','2025-04-19 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(24,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable Smooth acceleration and responsive braking Great for city driving and parking Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,3,19,NULL,'published','2024-12-03 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(25,'Absolutely fantastic! State-of-the-art amenities throughout Performed flawlessly under all conditions Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,26,46,NULL,'published','2025-05-28 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(26,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly Completely dependable for our entire trip Perfect companion for our business travel Will book with them again for sure.',4,10,99,NULL,'published','2025-11-05 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(27,'Absolutely fantastic! Premium features that enhanced every moment Absolutely perfect reliability record Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,2,54,NULL,'published','2025-01-07 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(28,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly Reliable performance throughout our trip Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is the car manual was missing. Highly recommend!',4,24,75,NULL,'published','2024-12-07 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(29,'Very pleased with this rental. The build quality was impressive Excellent customer service Excellent option for families Just a small issue with the owner\'s manual being missing but nothing major.',4,13,96,NULL,'published','2024-07-12 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(30,'Great rental experience! Great sound system The car was clean and well-maintained and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. Minor scuff on the bumper but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,7,92,NULL,'published','2025-06-12 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(31,'Excellent value for money. The infotainment system was user-friendly Performed consistently throughout our rental Reliable transportation for our family trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,22,83,NULL,'published','2025-08-04 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(32,'Below expectations. The radio presets weren\'t cleared The car was decent enough for basic needs but The pickup/return process. The pickup process was smooth but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,28,5,NULL,'published','2026-02-19 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(33,'Not great but manageable. The car felt underpowered on highways The basic features worked fine Would look for other options next time.',2,18,61,NULL,'published','2025-07-08 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(34,'Average rental experience. The car served its purpose adequately The pickup process took a while but the car was clean. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,16,67,NULL,'published','2025-12-21 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(35,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Completely dependable for our entire trip Reliable transportation for our family trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,23,18,NULL,'published','2024-05-12 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(36,'Decent car for the price. The interior space was adequate a small scuff on the rear bumper but overall acceptable for business trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,1,79,NULL,'published','2024-08-24 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(37,'Outstanding rental experience! Incredible fuel efficiency saved us money The car was absolutely pristine and was remarkably quiet and refined. Incredibly professional and courteous service Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,11,81,NULL,'published','2025-01-18 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(38,'Excellent value for money. The keyless entry was very convenient Never had a single mechanical issue Contributed to a memorable road trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,18,10,NULL,'published','2025-07-23 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(39,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly No unexpected problems or breakdowns Enhanced our weekend getaway experience Will book with them again for sure.',4,5,24,NULL,'published','2025-08-12 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(40,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles No unexpected problems or breakdowns Made our vacation stress-free and enjoyable Will book with them again for sure.',4,13,15,NULL,'published','2025-11-26 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(41,'Decent car for the price. The visibility was good one cup holder being a bit loose but overall acceptable for weekend getaway. Would consider again if needed.',3,23,3,NULL,'published','2025-03-25 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(42,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Incredibly comfortable for long drives Reliable performance throughout our trip Handled the mountain roads beautifully Only minor complaint is the car manual was missing. Highly recommend!',4,27,97,NULL,'published','2024-06-09 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(43,'Very pleased with this rental. High-quality materials and finishes Excellent customer service Will be my go-to rental company Just a small issue with a small scuff on the rear bumper but nothing major.',4,10,19,NULL,'published','2025-10-06 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(44,'Very pleased with this rental. Premium feel despite being a rental Made the rental process seamless Would definitely recommend to others Just a small issue with one cup holder being a bit loose but nothing major.',4,23,7,NULL,'published','2024-11-13 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(45,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine Outstanding professionalism and care Premium experience at a fair price Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,4,41,NULL,'published','2025-05-22 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(46,'Horrible condition vehicle. The tires were worn beyond safe limits I felt unsafe driving it. The windshield wipers were streaking badly Customer service was rude when I complained.',1,22,32,NULL,'published','2024-06-16 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(47,'Disappointing rental experience. The cleanliness standards was problematic and The brakes felt spongy and unsafe. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,16,18,NULL,'published','2025-11-26 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(48,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Very helpful with directions Great choice for anyone needing a reliable car Just a small issue with the owner\'s manual being missing but nothing major.',4,22,54,NULL,'published','2025-09-21 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(49,'Decent car for the price. The handling was predictable the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but overall acceptable for weekend getaway. Would consider again if needed.',3,15,56,NULL,'published','2024-09-20 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(50,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Started every time without hesitation Enhanced our weekend getaway experience Will book with them again for sure.',4,6,28,NULL,'published','2025-04-07 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(51,'Decent car for the price. The air conditioning was effective the pickup location being slightly hard to find but overall acceptable for family road trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,4,55,NULL,'published','2025-04-29 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(52,'Perfect car for our family road trip! The seats were like luxury recliners The performance was absolutely flawless Service that sets the gold standard Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,21,47,NULL,'published','2024-04-20 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(53,'Had some issues with this rental. The GPS system was completely outdated making the trip uncomfortable in hot weather The price was reasonable but the quality didn\'t match.',2,6,79,NULL,'published','2024-04-11 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(54,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was very reliable and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. The GPS was a bit outdated but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,26,25,NULL,'published','2026-02-21 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(55,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable The engine performed well on both city and highway Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,12,67,NULL,'published','2024-04-11 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(56,'Decent car for the price. The interior space was adequate the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but overall acceptable for conference. Would consider again if needed.',3,31,35,NULL,'published','2025-10-02 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(57,'Disappointing rental experience. The cleanliness standards was problematic and The air conditioning wasn\'t working properly. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,20,24,NULL,'published','2025-05-21 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(58,'Very pleased with this rental. High-quality materials and finishes Excellent customer service Will be my go-to rental company Just a small issue with the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but nothing major.',4,32,27,NULL,'published','2024-08-06 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(59,'Standard rental car. Adequate for the rental period The pickup process took a while Reasonable option for basic transportation Met basic expectations.',3,21,62,NULL,'published','2026-02-21 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(60,'Worst rental ever! The car wouldn\'t start after stopping for gas The car had electrical issues and I had to wait hours for assistance. Completely ruined my vacation. Avoid at all costs!',1,27,28,NULL,'published','2024-11-07 08:28:05','2026-03-06 08:28:05'),(61,'Absolutely fantastic! The technology was cutting-edge and intuitive Reliability that exceeded all expectations This rental exceeded every expectation This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,24,38,NULL,'published','2025-08-30 08:28:06','2026-03-06 08:28:06'),(62,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Very helpful with directions Perfect for business or leisure travel Just a small issue with the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but nothing major.',4,28,58,NULL,'published','2025-01-05 08:28:06','2026-03-06 08:28:06'),(63,'Not great but manageable. The exterior had several minor scratches The trunk space was adequate Would look for other options next time.',2,17,62,NULL,'published','2025-08-29 08:28:06','2026-03-06 08:28:06'),(64,'Disappointing rental experience. The vehicle\'s mechanical condition was problematic and The air conditioning wasn\'t working properly. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,3,87,NULL,'published','2025-07-29 08:28:06','2026-03-06 08:28:06');
